				<div itemprop="commentText" class='post entry-content '>
					Hi - this is an FYI...<br /> <br />Loaded the latest version of osc_sec.  We use IP_Trap.  Noticed osc_sec it was not sending emails any longer.  Looks like there needs to be a change in the email send function as it checks if banipaddress is set as well as send email but not if IP_Trap is set.  made the following change and it now works ....<br /> <br /><pre class='prettyprint lang-auto linenums:0'>
	    # send the notification
	    if ( (( false &#33;== ( bool )&#036;this-&gt;_banipaddress ) || (false &#33;== ( bool )&#036;this-&gt;_useIPTRAP )) &amp;&amp; ( false &#33;== ( bool )&#036;this-&gt;_emailenabled ) ) {
</pre>P<br /> <br />Peter
					
